片《灵异桑拿》而开始演艺生涯。2016年，她主演了漫改剧《镇魂街》。2018年，方楚彤凭借清装剧《延禧攻略》被众多观众认识。2019年，由其主演的校园喜剧《玛丽学园》播出。","name":"方楚彤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fang Chutong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"方楚彤","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"關曉彤，20 世紀 90 年代出生於廣東省潮汕地區，中國內地影視女演員。\n\n2015 年，關曉彤因主演懸疑片《靈異桑拿》而開始演藝生涯。2016 年，她主演了漫改劇《鎮魂街》。2018 年，關曉彤憑藉清裝劇《延禧攻略》被眾多觀眾認識。2019 年，由其主演的校園喜劇《瑪麗學園》播出。","name":"關曉彤","primary":false}}]}},"person_68763_translations":{"at":1774727018750,"data":{"id":68763,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Dean Winters (born July 20, 1964) is an American actor, who is known for his roles as Bobby on the YouTube series Wayne, Detective Brian Cassidy on Law & Order: SVU, Detective Russ Agnew on Battle Creek, 'The Vulture' Detective Pembroke on Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Charley Dixon on FOX's Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles, Dennis Duffy on NBC's 30 Rock, Johnny Gavin on FX's Rescue Me, Ryan O'Reily on HBO's Oz. He also portrays \"Mayhem\" in Allstate commercials.","name":"Dean Winters","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Dean Winters (narozen 20. července 1964) je americký herec, který ztvárnil Ryana O'Reilyho v seriálu Oz na HBO, Johnnyho Gavina v seriálu Zachraň mě na FX Network a Dennise Duffyho v seriálu Studio 30 Rock na NBC. V současné době také ztvárňuje postavu \"Mayhema\" v reklamách společnosti Allstate.\n\nVýše uvedený popis je převzat z článku Dean Winters na Wikipedii, licencováno pod CC-BY-SA, plný seznam přispěvatelů na Wikipedii.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（Dean Winters，1964年7月20日-）是一位美国演员，他因在YouTube系列剧《韦恩》中饰演鲍比，在《法律与秩序：SVU》中饰演侦探布莱恩·卡西迪，在《巴特尔克里克》中饰演侦探拉斯·阿格纽，在《布鲁克林九九》中饰演“秃鹫”侦探彭布罗克，在福克斯的《终结者：莎拉·康纳编年史》中饰演查理·迪克森，在NBC的《摇滚30》中饰演丹尼斯·达菲。 约翰尼·加文（Johnny Gavin）在FX的《拯救我》（Rescue Me）中，瑞安·奥雷利（Ryan O'Reily）在HBO的《绿野仙踪》（Oz）上。他还在 Allstate 广告中描绘了“混乱”。","name":"迪恩·温特斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ディーン・ウィンタース","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"딘 윈터스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（迪恩·温特斯，1964 年 7 月 20 日-）是一位美國演員，他因在 YouTube 系列劇《韋恩》中飾演鮑比，在《法律與秩序：SVU》中飾演偵探布萊恩·卡西迪，在《巴特爾克里克》中飾演偵探拉斯·阿格紐，在《布魯克林九九》中飾演“禿鷲”偵探彭布羅克，在福克斯的《未來戰士：莎拉·康納編年史》中飾演查理·迪克森，在 NBC 的《搖滾 30》中飾演丹尼斯·達菲。\n\n約翰尼·加文（Johnny Gavin）在 FX 的《拯救我》（Rescue Me）中，瑞安·奧雷利（Ryan O'Reily）在 HBO 的《綠野仙蹤》（Oz）上。他還在 Allstate 廣告中描繪了“混亂”。","name":"迪恩·温特斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дин Уинтерс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Dean Winters wurde am 20. Juli 1964 in New York City geboren und ist ein US-amerikanischer Schauspieler. Er wuchs auf Long Island auf und hat irische sowie italienische Vorfahren. Winters spricht fließend Italienisch. Seine Schauspielkarriere begann er 1996 mit einem Fernsehkurzfilm namens \"The Playroom\". Danach war er vor allem in Fernsehserien aktiv, unter anderem mit einer bedeutenden Rolle als Insasse Ryan O'Reily in der kultigen Gefängnisserie „Oz – Hölle hinter Gittern“ (1997–2003). Weitere bekannte Fernsehrollen spielte er in Serien wie „Law & Order: New York“ (1999–2000), „Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles“, „Rescue Me“ (2004–2011), wo er Johnny Gavin verkörperte, und „30 Rock“ (seit 2006 in Nebenrollen).\n\nWinters ist auch in vielen Filmen zu sehen, unter anderem als Avi in „John Wick“ (2014) sowie in „P.S. Ich liebe Dich“ (2007). Neben der Schauspielerei arbeitete er kurzzeitig als Model in Europa und absolvierte vor Beginn seiner Schauspielkarriere eine Zeit lang eine Barkeeper-Tätigkeit. Er hat drei jüngere Geschwister, darunter seinen Bruder Scott William Winters, ebenfalls Schauspieler.\n\nDean Winters gilt als vielseitiger Charakterdarsteller mit einer langjährigen Karriere im US-Fernsehen und -Film.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"דין ווינטרס","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дін Вінтерс","primary":false}}]}},"person_2948452_translations":{"at":1774727018820,"data":{"id":2948452,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wa Er","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"库都斯江·艾尼娃尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wa Er","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ва Эр","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"庫都斯江·艾尼娃爾","primary":false}}]}},"person_4357478_translations":{"at":1774727158041,"data":{"id":4357478,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чэнь Хуань","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chen Huan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳寰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陈寰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳寰","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1276704_keywords":{"at":1774727163816,"data":{"id":1276704,"keywords":[{"id":10181,"name":"based on play or musical"}]}},"person_1609473_translations":{"at":1774727166382,"data":{"id":1609473,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"黄柏钧（英文名：Denny Huang，1982年7月26日－），台湾男演员，出生于美国德州，从高中起就接受舞台剧、戏剧教育，从此激发他对表演的热情。回到台湾后，以模特儿身分出道，随后在2008年的偶像剧《不良笑花》中饰演男主角潘玮柏身边的无厘头助理赖瑞克，不计形象的搞笑演出令人印象深刻。除了演艺工作外，黄柏钧更是成功的经营者，拥有Marquee等餐厅。近年来，他帅气挺拔的外型也逐渐受到瞩目，也成功跨足电影圈，在2013年的电影《杀戒》中和刘烨、倪妮有精彩的对手戏。","name":"黄柏钧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Denny Huang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Denny Huang","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"黃柏鈞（英文名：Denny Huang，1982 年 7 月 26 日－），台灣男演員，出生於美國德州，從高中起就接受舞台劇、戲劇教育，從此激發他對錶演的熱情。回到台灣後，以模特兒身分出道，隨後在 2008 年的偶像劇《不良笑花》中飾演男主角潘瑋柏身邊的無釐頭助理賴瑞克，不計形象的搞笑演出令人印象深刻。除了演藝工作外，黃柏鈞更是成功的經營者，擁有 Marquee 等餐廳。近年來，他帥氣挺拔的外型也逐漸受到矚目，也成功跨足電影圈，在 2013 年的電影《殺戒》中和劉燁、倪妮有精彩的對手戲。","name":"黃柏鈞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Хуан Бо Цзюнь","primary":false}}]}},"person_1116027_translations":{"at":1774727168524,"data":{"id":1116027,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Adam Boncz","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"亚当·邦茨","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Адам Бонч","primary":false}}]}}}}